                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>minn-hum yaʕṭī-h aḷḷa ʕəmr-un ṭawīl, yaʕṭī-h aḷḷa aʕmāl-in ṭayyba w minn-hum... law inn-ah muslim lāzim yḥuwš ḏanb, yʕaḏḏib išwayy w yiǧmaʕ lē-h, mā-fī xalāf, yā bint-i ((noun adjective structure - note antonella tanwīn esperta) </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
